summary: AN ORDINANCE repealing Ordinance 109182 which created Local Improvement District No. 6724 for the improvement of The Alley in Block M, "Dumar's Highland Park" Addition and in Block M, Supplemental Plat of Blocks A-B-C-G-Lots 1 and 12 Block F and Lots 1 and 24 Block M, Dumar's Highland Park Addition, being a continuous alley between 12th Avenue Southwest and 11th Avenue Southwest from Southwest Holden Street to Southwest Webster Street, by paving, etc.
